## About This Template

This is a production-ready monorepo template created by **Piar Concept** to help 
startups and businesses quickly launch modern web applications with:

- Multiple Next.js applications (public website + backoffice)
- Serverless functions ready
- Shared packages architecture
- Complete testing infrastructure
- ESLint configuration
- TypeScript strict mode
- Turbo build system with caching
- AI-friendly documentation

